						<summary>

						<p>Slab built in the floor of the Baḍigēra well (1).</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">17th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This damaged record probably recorded the excavation of a well by Basavappa son of Chyanamma.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in the cyclic year Jaya, Chaitra, śu. 6. The Śaka year is not mentioned. It is in characters of the 17th century A.D. </p>						

